{% extends "partials/base.html.twig" %}

{% set pageTitle = 'FAQ' %}

{% block content %}
    <section class="readable-text">
        <h2>FAQ</h2> <!-- LEARN JAVASCRIPT AND CREATE ACCORDION MENUS.-->
        <ol>
            <li>
                <h3>I am lost and I need context. What is "HZ" and what exactly is this website?</h3>
                <p>This is a showcase portfolio website. It is the result of the very first assignment I
                    received at my college HBO-ICT programme. In addition, it's the first website I've ever
                    made. Please be kind. :&rpar;</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>How can you print a document from your laptop at HZ?</h3>
                <p>Go to <a href="https://hz.mynetpay.nl/" target="_blank">https://hz.mynetpay.nl/</a>, log
                    in to your HZ-account, put money on your HZ-card, drop files into the drop area and set
                    the proper settings before uploading them. Walk to the nearest printing press and swipe
                    your card over the scanning area.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>How can you scan a document and send it to your laptop at HZ?</h3>
                <p>Scanning documents is free. Swipe your card over the printing press' scanning area and
                    select "scanning" from the menu. Put your thing inside the scanning comportant, commence
                    the scanning and send it to your account or whatever. A toddler can figure out how to do
                    it. </p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>How can I buy something (like when I sign up for the IT introduction event) on the HZ
                    web
                    shop?</h3>
                <p>First, log in to your personal MyHZ Portal. Second, navigate to your personal menu
                    settings,
                    and add the 'Webshop' widget to the menu, save it, then go back to your dashboard and
                    click
                    on the link. If you have ever ordered any item anywhere on the item, then you'll know
                    where
                    to go from here.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>How can you book a project space?</h3>
                <p>First, log in to your personal MyHZ Portal. Second, navigate to your personal menu
                    settings,
                    and add the 'Self Service Portal' widget to the menu, save it, then go back to your
                    dashboard and click
                    on the link. Click on the 'Reservations' square, click on the 'How do I make a
                    reservation?'
                    square if you require further instructions, otherwise just click on the 'Reserve a
                    meeting
                    or project room' square.</p>
            </li>
            <li>
                <h3>What are the instructions if you want to park your car at the HZ parking lot?</h3>
                <div class="text-acc-figure">
                    <div>
                        <p>For Het Groene Woud:</p>
                        <p>Instruction #1: Have some sort of disability or chronic condition.</p>
                        <p>Instruction #2: Profit.</p>
                        <p>Otherwise:</p>
                        <p>Instruction #1: Park at Parkeergarage Kousteensedijk, Middelburg.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div>
                        <figure class="captioned-figure">
                            <img src="/resources/1673d955-7c0f-4ebb-92cc-39e9f6a873eb.jpeg"
                                 alt="Parking Garage Photo">
                            <div></div>
                            <figcaption>Able-bodied PUNKS park here.</figcaption>
                        </figure>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </section>
{% endblock %}